Alembic migrations for BookMyDoctor.

Common commands (run from the backend/ directory, venv active):

  # autogenerate a migration after changing app/models.py
  alembic revision --autogenerate -m "describe change"

  # apply migrations up to latest
  alembic upgrade head

  # roll back one step
  alembic downgrade -1

The DB URL comes from app.config.settings (DATABASE_URL env var); it is not
hardcoded in alembic.ini.
